ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:56:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有可能係扮有精神問題,博唔駛入普通監獄而係入小欖/青山 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係裏面都唔錯啊,至少咩都唔使煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}